name: PrincePhillipQuotes
0:
”Alexa, ask prince phillip quotes for a funny quote”
”Give me a quote”
”Give me a Prince Phillip quote”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: prince phillip quotes
des:
Hello old chap, want to hear some funny old quotes by the one and only Prince Phillip? You've come to the right skill! Over 100 great and cheeky quotes for you to hear and many more to come as we update the app. 

To get the app started just "Alexa ask Prince Phillip Quotes for a quote " and one will be provided.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
